item.title: Will anyone tell me how to get client.java?!?!?!?!?!?!?!
item.dc:creator: @lothy Lothy
item.description:
@lothy wrote:

When you open your source, there will be either one or two files called ‘client’. If you have one, double click it, and congrats you’ve found your client.java; If you have two, double click both. The one that has readable words and not [] like things all over the place is client.java.

If this is too much for you I suggest you just play someone else’s server.
